text: Seo Hun-gyo (born 16 June 1944) is a South Korean wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 70 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of South Korea Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Busan
